profile:
If you aren’t hiring a cleaning specialist, your home isn’t clean. 

At Fern and Fox Cleaning, we know that you want to walk into your home confident that it is clean and fresh. 

The problem is that many cleaners are inconsistent and lack the tools and training to do a truly thorough job, which leaves you wondering if the work was done well. We believe that you shouldn’t have to second guess the work your cleaner has done. 

We understand that you care about having a clean home free of dirt and allergens, that you can confidently bring the most discerning guests into. This is why we invested in specialist training and the best tools in the industry. 

Here is how you can enjoy the confidence of a Fern and Fox clean: 

Post-Construction Clean:
1.Go online to fernandfoxcleaning.com for a free estimate.
2.We follow up within 1 business day.
3.You get our 70-point cleaning checklist clean, everytime! 
Area Rug:

1.Go online to book a pick-up time.
2.We do the hard work! 
3.You enjoy a like-new rug knowing your kids and pets are safe (and your mother-in-law will be impressed!) 

There really isn’t any reason to doubt that the cleaners you hired didn’t execute the job with excellence. 

At Fern and Fox Cleaning we want to take the stress of tedious work off your shoulders. We want you to experience the difference speciality cleaning can make. 

Go to fernandfoxcleaning.com to get your free estimate now!
